the expression of the emotions in man an.data-term: the expression of the emotions in man and animals

examples.en: John yawned and scratched his leg.
She yawned and rubbed her eyes.
The pit yawned open in front of them.
The child yawned during the long performance.
He yawned, closed his eyes again, and turned over.
Carl sat up in bed, yawned, and stretched.
